OL,3,CJersey parents asked to apply for
OL,4,C'Back to School Bonus' payments
OL,6,FApplications are open for the
OL,7,FGovernment of Jersey's "Back to School
OL,8,FBonus" programme, which aims to help
OL,9,Fparents pay for school supplies.
OL,11,FThe funding, announced in April, will
OL,12,F"support islanders with the cost of
OL,13,Fliving pressures", according to
OL,14,Fofficials.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
