OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781801274
OL,3,CJersey parents asked to apply for
OL,4,C'Back to School Bonus' payments
OL,6,FUnder the last government, Jersey's
OL,7,FSocial Security Minister, Deputy
OL,8,FLyndsay Feltham, said "it's important
OL,9,Fthat we help where we can to ease any
OL,10,Ffinancial stress on families by
OL,11,Fensuring children across the island
OL,12,Fhave the essentials they need for the
OL,13,Fnew school year".
OL,15,FOnly households with a total income of
OL,16,F#75,000 or lower last year, and with
OL,17,Fat least one child entering any class
OL,18,Fbetween reception and Year 11 in
OL,19,FJersey this September, can apply.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1781801274
OL,3,CJersey parents asked to apply for
OL,4,C'Back to School Bonus' payments
OL,6,FFamilies also need to have lived in
OL,7,FJersey since at least 30 September
OL,8,F2025.
OL,10,FThe Government is offering those
OL,11,Feligible #100 per primary school-aged
OL,12,Fchild and #150 if their son or
OL,13,Fdaughter is in secondary education -
OL,14,Fthere is no limit on the number of
OL,15,Fchildren a family can claim for.
OL,17,FFamilies that already receive income
OL,18,Fsupport will get the extra money
OL,19,Fautomatically and do not need to apply.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
