OL,3,CJersey parents asked to apply for
OL,4,C'Back to School Bonus' payments
OL,6,FSubmissions close for everyone else on
OL,7,FFriday 31 July, with those who are
OL,8,Feligible receiving one lump sum in
OL,9,FAugust ahead of the new school year.
OL,11,FDetails of how to apply can be found
OL,12,Fhere.
